184
00:11:24,650 --> 00:11:25,370
Yes.

185
00:11:32,690 --> 00:11:33,940
In my dream,

186
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:37,220
the same pattern

187
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:40,160
was on the hilt of the sword

188
00:11:43,490 --> 00:11:46,400
