189
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:20,010
Can't fall asleep?

190
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:28,930
Are you thinking about that nightmare?

191
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:33,390
Yes.

192
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:37,670
Don't worry.

193
00:12:38,330 --> 00:12:39,970
