235
00:15:44,670 --> 00:15:45,490
It's fine.

236
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:47,530
Mo Yan said he and I would go for a spring outing today.

237
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:49,120
It'll be easy and relaxing.

238
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:50,390
But you just...

239
