265
00:16:58,050 --> 00:16:59,550
To be honest,

266
00:16:59,850 --> 00:17:01,200
Mount Niuyang

267
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:02,580
is full of spiritual energy.

268
00:17:02,730 --> 00:17:04,369
For us demons,

269
00:17:04,430 --> 00:17:06,460
